name: Dogtown
description: Dogtown is a Combat Zone and one of the sub-districts of Pacifica, located in southern Night City. Before the creation of Dogtown, this area was known as Serenisands. Dogtown is exclusive to Cyberpunk 2077: Phantom Liberty and will become accessible during the quest Dog Eat Dog.
